{
  "texts": [
    "To ensure the validity of our experiments, we randomly selected 20 vertices as the set of query vertices.",
    "The topic similarity threshold is set from 0.5 to 0.95, and the k is set from 1 to 12.",
    "In the results reported in the following, each data point is the average result for these queries.",
    "From the parameter analysis section in paper, we have analyzed that a larger k and mean denser topology.",
    "In order to identify intermediatesized dense communities surrounding query vertices in the DBLP and ASN datasets, we determined appropriate parameter configurations to be k = 9 and = 0.60, and 0.95, respectively (the settings of Table 3 in paper)."
  ]
}